					<dt class="comment" id="comment-532149">
						<span class="comment_num"><a href="#comment-532149" title="Permalink to this comment" rel="nofollow">103</a></span>
						<p><span class="comment_author">adam.smith</span> <span class="comment_time">06.01.14 at 7:46 pm</span></p>
					</dt>
					<dd class="comment">
						<div class="format_text">
<p>@J Thomas #101<br />
