					<dd class="comment alt">
						<div class="format_text">
<p>And of course I&#8217;m not forgetting (though I seem to) that what happens in coming centuries may be chaos, if we don&#8217;t get our act together on climate change.</p>
<p>A seductive thing about climate change is that the &#8216;warm period&#8217; which many of us seem to be experiencing at present is actually quite pleasant &#8211; the brief earlier burst of heatwaves and fires (which I believe you are already having in parts of the US) all but forgotten in the extended mild autumn we are having here in southern Australia. But it&#8217;s becoming unseasonable &#8211; starting to feel wrong.</p>
